import React from 'react'
import './SongEdit.css'
import { Edit, SimpleForm, TextInput, DateInput, FileInput, FileField } from 'react-admin'


const SongEdit = (props) => {
  return (
    <Edit title='Edit Song' {...props}>
      <SimpleForm >
        <TextInput className="focus" disabled source='id' />
        <TextInput className="focus" source='song_name'  />
        <TextInput className="focus" source='song_duration'/>
        <DateInput className="focus" source='date_added' />  
        <TextInput className="focus" source='stream_count' style={{border:'orange'}}/>
        <FileInput className="focus" source="files" label="Path" >
          <FileField className="focus" source="src" title="title" />
        </FileInput>
        <TextInput source="song_image" />
      </SimpleForm>
    </Edit>
  )
}

export default SongEdit
